             was indicted for <rs id="t17921215-113-off621" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17921215-113-off621" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17921215-113-off621" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17921215-113-cd622" type="crimeDate">14th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17921215-113-off621 t17921215-113-cd622"></join>, ten yards of cotton, value 35 s. four cotton shawls, value 12 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17921215-113-victim1196" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Scoffeld
                        <interp inst="t17921215-113-victim1196" type="surname" value="Scoffeld"></interp>
