                     <interp inst="t17921215-113-verdict625" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               GUILTY of stealing to the value 39 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17921215-113-punish626" type="punishmentDescription">
